This repository contains a script to generate a TSV file by retrieving
translations from the dictionary on Lernu. Then, the file can be
formatted using the filter and inserted into Anki.
The Makefile automates file generation.

Usage :

	./script [language] < words.txt > tsv.txt 2>&1
	./filter < tsv.txt > cards.txt

Language codes (from Lernu):

  - ar (العربية),
  - bg (Български),
  - ca (Català),
  - cs (Česky),
  - da (Dansk),
  - de (Deutsch),
  - el (Ελληνικά),
  - en (English),
  - es (Español),
  - fa (فارسی),
  - fi (Suomi),
  - fr (Français),
  - he (עברית),
  - hi (हिन्दी),
  - hr (Hrvatski),
  - hsb (Hornjoserbsce),
  - hu (Magyar),
  - id (Bahasa Indonesia),
  - it (Italiano),
  - ja (日本語),
  - lt (Lietuvių),
  - nl (Nederlands),
  - no (Norsk bokmål),
  - pl (Polski),
  - pt (Português),
  - ro (Română),
  - ru (Русский),
  - sk (Slovenčina),
  - sl (Slovenščina),
  - sv (Svenska),
  - sw (Kiswahili),
  - th (ไทย),
  - tl (Tagalog),
  - tr (Türkçe),
  - uk (Українська),
  - vi (Tiếng Việt),
  - zh-cn (简体中文),
  - zh (中文),

Please note that the dictionary is very limited for some languages.

Dependencies:

  - php
  - php-curl
